title: Get Week 6 high school football updates here, no poncho needed
text:
You can keep the rain gear in the closet and follow high school football games here. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Kyle Craig | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 09, 2015 5:50 PM, updated October 09, 2015 6:45 PM View/Post Comments 
There's no reason to get soggy while searching for your high school football fix. 
Lehighvalleylive.com is compiling updates from stadiums in the Lehigh Valley and northwestern New Jersey, and bringing them all to you in one place. 
Touchdowns, turnovers, etc., will be relayed as they happen. 
Follow updates from reporters and athletic departments in the comments section at the bottom of this post to stay informed on games from across the region.
